text: Aust-Agder (, ) was a county (fylke) in Norway until 1 January 2020. It was merged with Vest-Agder to form Agder county. In 2002, there were 102,945 people living here. ==Other websites== *Political map *Aust-Agder fylkeskommune (in English) *Photogallery * Category:Former counties of Norway Category:Agder
